data.description: This spacious all brick home sits on nearly an acre lot with lots of yard space for recreation. Positioned on a quiet cul-de-sac in a peaceful, country setting, backing up to a gorgeous pond, this house features hardwood and tiled floors with NO carpeting. The vaulted ceiling great room has a new ceiling fan, gas fireplace, and hardwood floors. Many updates have been done by the sellers throughout the house. This is one you need to see in person to appreciate. The screened porch may be the best part of this house, with its tiled floor and private and beautiful views. The house also boasts a tiled sunroom, huge master bedroom, and a two car garage with no step into the house. This low maintenance house will delight young and old with its friendly floor plan and location with almost no traffic. Come see today!
